[1]Ndirĩ na ũhurũko,Ndĩ gũkũ thĩ-ĩno ndĩ rũgendo-inĩNdorete matu-inĩ.Nĩtũkoima thĩ-ĩno,Twambate igũrũ,Mũciĩ ũcio mũtheru nĩguo tũgatũra[2]Mathĩna ma thĩ-ĩno,Na mbara cia thĩ-ĩno,Ciothe nĩigathira.[3]Ikaragai mwĩ thĩinĩ,Wa Roho Mũtheru,Tondũ ena maithori,Ma ngoro iria iguĩte.[4]Roho nĩaratwĩra,Tũtige maciira.Na ndundu ciothe,Nama nĩigathira.[5]Menyai wega nama,Arĩa mũrĩ thĩinĩ.Wa ngwatanĩro,Ndĩ hamwe na inyuĩ.[6]Ngumwĩra nama,Mũiyũrwo nĩ wendo.Tondũ Roho Mutheru,Aĩyuirwo nĩ wendo.[7]Thagathagai ngoro ciikare ũtheru-inĩ.Tondũ Jesũ witũ,Ehakuhĩ.
